00:03.502 --> 00:04.702
There you go, Billy.

00:04.704 --> 00:06.404
Enjoy those Boston creams.

00:06.406 --> 00:07.671
And no judgments.

00:07.673 --> 00:08.906
Everyone deserves a cheat day.

00:08.908 --> 00:10.174
Yeah.

00:11.176 --> 00:13.277
Wow. Look at all this cash, huh?

00:13.279 --> 00:14.846
Boy, business has been great
the last two weeks.

00:14.848 --> 00:16.047
I wonder what's going on?

00:16.049 --> 00:17.715
Hmm. You think it was the addition

00:17.717 --> 00:19.584
