00:26.993 --> 00:29.961
Oh. I'm gonna be late for class.

00:29.963 --> 00:32.597
- You going back to school, Tush?
- Yep.

00:32.598 --> 00:34.465
When you're a self-employed
Renaissance man

00:34.467 --> 00:37.235
like myself, you've always got
to be expanding your skill set,

00:37.237 --> 00:40.138
- so I'm learning to draw caricatures.
- Dope.

00:40.140 --> 00:41.506
A fellow artist.

00:41.508 --> 00:43.574
I'm hoping to get a gig
down at Navy Pier.

00:43.576 --> 00:45.910
You see, caricature artists
are kind of like the rock stars

00:45.912 --> 00:47.745
of the street performer community.

00:47.747 --> 00:50.047
They get way more tail
than bucket drummers.

00:50.049 --> 00:51.616
Oh, right, yeah.

00:51.618 --> 00:53.017
Let me see them.

00:53.019 --> 00:54.385
Oh, there you go.

00:54.387 --> 00:56.420
Oh, is that you?

00:56.422 --> 00:58.823
- And are those bees?
- Yeah.

00:58.825 --> 01:01.726
First rule of caricature:
give the people a hobby.

01:01.728 --> 01:03.427
And I'm a beekeeper.

01:03.429 --> 01:06.697
