got the queen in the divorce,

01:06.699 --> 01:10.301
- and all the bees followed her home.
- Oh.

01:10.303 --> 01:13.804
- I bet that really stung.
- Hey.

01:13.806 --> 01:15.773
- Too soon.
- I'm sorry.

01:15.775 --> 01:18.509
- Well, have a great class.
- Thank you.

01:18.511 --> 01:20.912
Tonight we're learning
to draw décolletage,

01:20.914 --> 01:23.314
that's French for "upper boobs."

01:25.318 --> 01:26.784
- Oh, I'm beat.
- Yeah.

01:26.786 --> 01:28.219
Last thing I want to
do is walk six blocks

01:28.221 --> 01:30.354
to the bank and make this deposit.

01:30.356 --> 01:31.622
Well, I can do it for you.

01:31.624 --> 01:32.823
Uh, no. No, that's okay.

01:32.825 --> 01:34.358
I don't want to put you out.

01:34.360 --> 01:36.194
No, it's cool. I walk by your
bank on my way home.

01:36.196 --> 01:38.918
- No. I got it.
- Seriously, I don't mind.

01:38.943 --> 01:40.965
- It's windy as hell out there.
- No. It's all right.

01:40.967 --> 01:43.968
My doctor says I'm not
getting enough wind.

01:43.970 --> 01:46.204
Wait, wait, wait. Hold on.

01:46.206 --> 01:47.805
You don't trust me, do you?

01:47.807 --> 01:49.173
No, no, no.

01:49.175 --> 01:51.609
