01:51.611 --> 01:53.678
Wow. All right.

01:53.680 --> 01:55.513
No, no, no, no.
Don't take it personally.

01:55.515 --> 01:57.081
I mean, you just started two weeks ago.

01:57.083 --> 01:58.482
I hardly know you.

01:58.484 --> 01:59.517
What are you talking about?

01:59.519 --> 02:00.818
I told you everything about myself.

02:00.820 --> 02:02.653
My hopes, my dreams...

02:02.655 --> 02:04.854
- even that time my dad threw me out.
- Maybe it's because

02:04.879 --> 02:07.592
you wouldn't shut up
about your hopes and dreams.

02:07.594 --> 02:09.926
Seriously, why don't you trust
me, hmm? 'Cause I'm young?

02:09.929 --> 02:12.563
'Cause I smoke weed?
'Cause I've done graffiti?

