07:00.019 --> 07:01.185
Can you help me find him?

07:01.187 --> 07:02.219
Yeah, sure, man.

07:02.221 --> 07:03.387
Whoa.

07:03.389 --> 07:04.722
Give me your backpack.

07:04.724 --> 07:06.023
I can't man, listen.

07:06.025 --> 07:08.192
But I'll give you
everything in my wallet.

07:08.194 --> 07:11.295
No. Don't make me use this, man.

07:11.297 --> 07:13.297
- Is that your finger?
- No.

07:13.299 --> 07:15.232
- Yes, it is.
- Mm-mm!

07:15.234 --> 07:16.467
I know that voice.

07:16.469 --> 07:19.236
- Is that you Crackhead Kevin?
- No.

07:19.238 --> 07:20.571
I'm a different crackhead.

07:20.573 --> 07:23.340
You don't know me,
now give me the bag, Franco.

07:23.342 --> 07:24.675
I told you I can't, all right?

07:24.677 --> 07:26.377
So do you want the wallet or not?

07:26.379 --> 07:28.212
Okay, fine.

07:31.484 --> 07:34.785
Damn. You got unexpected
crackhead strength, Kevin!

07:34.787 --> 07:37.221
Don't judge me... you don't know
where my regular strength ends

07:37.223 --> 07:38.756
and my crackhead strength begins.

07:42.562 --> 07:44.700
You called an Uber?

07:52.432 --> 07:54.225
Oh, my God, what happened to you?

07:54.227 --> 07:55.627
I got jumped.

07:55.629 --> 07:57.762
They took my backpack
with all your money it.

07:57.764 --> 07:59.248
And I tried to stop him but
he threw me against this gate...

07:59.273 --> 08:00.332
Try-try not to talk.

08:00.334 --> 08:01.399
Why, am I losing a lot of blood?

08:01.401 --> 08:02.867
No, because it's annoying.

08:02.869 --> 08:04.703
Did you get, did you get
a good look at the guy?

08:04.705 --> 08:06.905
Yeah, it's a dude from the
neighborhood, Crackhead Kevin.

08:06.907 --> 08:11.476
Crackhead Debbie's son? Boy the pipe
doesn't fall far from the tree. Come on.

08:11.478 --> 08:13.478
Is everything okay?
I noticed the lights on

08:13.480 --> 08:15.647
when I was helping
a man in a wheelchair...

08:15.649 --> 08:18.883
get out of an apartment
I was evicting him from.

08:18.885 --> 08:21.219
Franco got mugged.
They took the deposit bag.

08:21.221 --> 08:23.688
- With the $700 in it.
- Don't worry about that now.

08:23.690 --> 08:24.823
The important thing is you're okay.

08:24.825 --> 08:26.257
Now go on, clean up that wound.

08:26.259 --> 08:27.692
I'm sorry, man.

08:27.694 --> 08:29.694
How interesting.

08:29.696 --> 08:31.363
The first night
you give him the deposit,

08:31.365 --> 08:33.063
he is mugged.

08:33.066 --> 08:35.467
Notice my quotes in air.

08:35.469 --> 08:37.402
He didn't take the money, Fawz.

08:37.404 --> 08:39.304
- How do you know?
- Because if he took it

08:39.306 --> 08:40.672
he would-he would have counted it,

08:40.674 --> 08:44.743
and realized that I only put $30 in it.

08:44.745 --> 08:46.678
I don't understand.

08:46.680 --> 08:48.580
It was a test. I was
gonna take the rest of it

08:48.582 --> 08:50.148
