how much was in the bag.

09:15.675 --> 09:18.243
Your secret is safe.

09:18.245 --> 09:20.245
Be cool, be cool.

09:20.247 --> 09:21.679
- Be cool... put a foot...
- Uh, uh...

09:21.681 --> 09:23.415
- All right, which one?
- Pick a side!

09:23.417 --> 09:26.351
- Arthur, Franco just called.
- Is he okay?

09:26.353 --> 09:29.054
There's nothing you can prove!

09:29.056 --> 09:31.589
Just a couple guys talking
about <i>Sex and the City.</i>

09:31.591 --> 09:33.492
Stop it.

09:34.060 --> 09:35.226
He got banged up a little bit.

09:35.228 --> 09:36.661
He's in the bathroom washing up.

09:36.663 --> 09:39.531
- Hey. Thanks for getting here so quick.
- No problem.

09:39.533 --> 09:40.701
- Just tell us what happened.
- Okay.

09:40.726 --> 09:42.833
Starting with exactly
how much was stolen.

09:42.858 --> 09:44.636
Well, it was $700. Right, Arthur?

09:44.638 --> 09:46.471
Well, maybe,
you know, a little bit more.

09:46.473 --> 09:48.773
