10:56.676 --> 10:58.776
Or I'll get another job.

10:58.778 --> 10:59.844
Or I'll sell my Jordans.

10:59.846 --> 11:01.112
Will you stop?

11:01.114 --> 11:02.480
Dude, let me make this up to you.

11:02.482 --> 11:04.749
You-you gave me a job,
and I screwed up. All right?

11:04.751 --> 11:07.118
And I'm-I'm not gonna rest
till I get your $700 back.

11:07.120 --> 11:09.420
Look, it wasn't $700.

11:09.422 --> 11:11.923
It was $30, okay?

11:12.073 --> 11:13.555
Wait...

11:13.743 --> 11:15.431
- Wait, what are you talking about?
- Look,

11:15.629 --> 11:18.493
I was just trying to find out
if I could trust you. All right?

11:19.199 --> 11:21.099
So this was some sort of test?

11:21.101 --> 11:23.001
Yeah, but the good news is you passed.

11:23.003 --> 11:25.103
Hmm? So, yay.

11:25.105 --> 11:27.205
I can trust you now.

11:27.207 --> 11:29.807
Put 'er there, homie.

11:29.809 --> 11:32.810
I can't believe you, man.

11:34.714 --> 11:36.814
But...

11:40.019 --> 11:43.087
Hey, wouldn't it be funny
if he got mugged again?

11:43.089 --> 11:45.883
Not ha-ha funny. Ironic!

11:51.879 --> 11:53.534
Oh, hey! There he is!

11:53.559 --> 11:55.845
Some may say he's ten minutes late,

11:55.847 --> 11:58.381
but I say he's ten minutes great!

11:58.383 --> 11:59.649
Drop it, Arthur.

11:59.651 --> 12:01.918
Oh. Hey, hey, come on.

12:01.920 --> 12:04.387
I said I'm sorry
about yesterday, all right?

12:04.389 --> 12:05.655
Did you get my texts?

12:05.657 --> 12:07.256
- Nope.
- Really?

12:07.258 --> 12:09.726
I sent you a bunch of them
telling you how terrible I felt.

12:09.728 --> 12:12.528
I also sent you a sad face
and a peace sign.

12:12.530 --> 12:15.298
And a Japanese flag,
but that was an accident.

12:15.300 --> 12:16.699
Well, I didn't get 'em.

12:16.701 --> 12:17.800
Well, who did?

12:17.802 --> 12:19.802
Arthur, thank you for your texts.

12:19.804 --> 12:23.039
I don't know what you did,
but of course I forgive you.

12:23.041 --> 12:25.708
